        <I>point(i)</I>, with <MATH><I>i&gt;0</I></MATH>, is different from the 
        source.<BR>

<EM>Precondition: </EM><MATH><I>i  <IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=11 HEIGHT=25 ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="cc_geq.gif"> 0</I></MATH>.
